t active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\n\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\n\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, blocker appeared, task completed), compose a concise change report to group -5163901258:\n\nFormat:\n🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nChanges detected:\n• [list of actual changes]\n\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\n• Active sessions: N\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: none / [list blockers]\n\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 15th, 2026 - 5:30 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-15 05:30 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776231078793,"__openclaw":{"id":"02db3c5a","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the current state of active sessions and compare against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bc6wnmssn2yg_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"kinds":["agent"],"limit":20,"messageLimit":2}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bc6wnmssn2yg_2","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"heartbeat-state"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":438,"output":98,"totalTokens":14480,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776231078992,"responseId":"062e55a8b5e9884a0d36b8da43a7c982","__openclaw":{"id":"ed393ac3","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"tel